---
const sizes = "(min-width: 1024px) 22rem, 18rem"; // md:w-88 else w-72
---
<section class="py-16">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="relative rounded-[28px] bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-50 to-white border border-black/5 shadow-sm p-6 md:p-10 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -z-10 top-10 left-6 w-56 h-40 bg-black/5 rounded-2xl"></div>
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -z-10 top-16 left-12 w-64 h-44 bg-black/10 rounded-2xl"></div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-center">
        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -z-10 -top-3 -left-3 w-full h-full rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-black/10"></div>
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl ring-1 ring-black/10 inline-block">
              <picture>
                <source type="image/webp" srcset="/clinic-stack-640.webp 640w, /clinic-stack-960.webp 960w" sizes={sizes} />
                <img src="/clinic-stack-960.jpg" alt="D‑Essence Wellness treatment room"
                     class="block w-72 md:w-88 h-auto object-cover object-center" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
              </picture>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:col-span-7">
          <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <div class="text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-600">MED SPA IN NEW WINDSOR, NY</div>
            <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Reflect Your Best Self<br/>With Exceptional Medical Aesthetics</h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-[15px] leading-7 text-neutral-800">
              At D‑Essence Wellness, we believe true beauty begins with confidence. Our medical aesthetic center at
              <strong>871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102, New Windsor, NY 12553</strong> offers a welcoming and
              professional environment designed to enhance your natural features and care for your skin with the highest standards.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-7 text-neutral-800">
              Our non‑surgical, minimally invasive treatments combine advanced technology and personalized protocols to deliver safe, natural results.
              From aesthetic injectables and full‑face rejuvenation to peels, regenerative therapies, and advanced skin care, we focus on your overall well‑being and transformative experiences.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-6 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4 flex gap-3">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" /><path d="M8 12h8M12 8v8" /></svg>
                <div><div class="text-sm font-semibold">Advanced Injectables</div><div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Subtle, refined results.</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4 flex gap-3">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M4 12h16M12 4v16" /><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" /></svg>
                <div><div class="text-sm font-semibold">Full‑Face Rejuvenation</div><div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Face‑as‑a‑whole harmony.</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4 flex gap-3">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M4 16l8-8 8 8" /></svg>
                <div><div class="text-sm font-semibold">Laser & Skin Tech</div><div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Resurfacing & innovation.</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4 flex gap-3">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M7 12l3 3 7-7" /></svg>
                <div><div class="text-sm font-semibold">Certified Care</div><div class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Warm, expert experience.</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-8">
              <a href="/appointment" class="relative text-sm font-medium tracking-wide"><span class="pb-1 border-b border-black inline-block">Book a Consultation</span></a>
              <a href="/services" class="text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:text-black underline underline-offset-4">View all services</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
